<br>
I have seen people try to increase the value of the spell saying it was overly rare and asking for 2k, but generally it seems at best it is a &quot;semi-rare&quot; spell and is usually available with a day or two of searching in the 500pp price if you are looking to purchase.<br>
<br>
While it is one of our more useful spells, thankfully it seems to be reasonably available. <p><table border="0" >
